      "body" : "Tysvm for this table. I have reified and extended it into a Google Sheet document I&#39;ve shared here: <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1HzSpbHhaB6igjkc0me2hTYehgfNkYCENw7io7IQI9vM/edit?usp=sharing\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/&hellip;</a>"
